      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四八卦旗、张飞、赵云、黄忠、魏延引诸葛亮同上。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017009_e00002",
      "play_id": "01017009",
      "scene_id": "01017009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "点绛唇",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "八卦阴阳，安排停当，统兵将，出离荆襄，要把西川掌。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017009_e00003",
      "play_id": "01017009",
      "scene_id": "01017009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "自幼隐居卧龙岗，阴阳八卦袖内藏。桃园武艺无人挡，擒却张任灭刘璋。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017009_e00004",
      "play_id": "01017009",
      "scene_id": "01017009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "山人，诸葛亮。奉了主公之命，攻打雒城。只因张任，武艺高强，颇有胆略。必须擒了此人，大兵方可前进。黄忠听令。",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017009_e00005",
      "play_id": "01017009",
      "scene_id": "01017009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
